-- Sorrell’s WPP Pay Package May Be Reviewed, Sunday Telegraph Says
-- B y   C a t h e r i n e   A i r l i e
-- 2012-06-10T09:37:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-10/sorrell-s-wpp-pay-package-may-be-reviewed-sunday-telegraph-says.html
WPP Plc (WPP) ’s Chief Executive Officer
Martin Sorrell may have his pay package reviewed after a June 13
meeting in Dublin, The Sunday Telegraph reported.  Shareholders views will be taken into account when
reviewing Sorrell’s almost 13 million pounds ($20 million)
compensation package during the company’s annual general
meeting, the newspaper reported, citing an interview with Philip
Lader, chairman of the media company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
